sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Python as [Python Package]
  participant Backend as [Backend]
  participant DB as [DB]
  participant Redis as [Redis]
  participant MTX as [MediaMTX :8888]

  opt discover HLS port
    Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/info
    Note over Python,Backend: Auth 불필요<br/>Response urls.hls_port = 8888
    Backend-->>Python: server info
  end

  Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/live-streams
  Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token

  Backend->>Backend: requireDashboardOrAppOrPython
  Backend->>DB: readable repository ids 계산
  Note over Backend,DB: admin은 전체 repository read 가능<br/>일반 사용자는 repo_members와 public repository 기준

  Backend->>Redis: active stream cache 조회
  Note over Backend,Redis: set: stream:active:sessions<br/>MGET: stream:recording:{recordingSessionId}<br/>required cache status: STREAMING

  Backend-->>Python: 200 { streams }
  Note over Backend,Python: item fields<br/>recording_session_id<br/>repository_id<br/>repository_name<br/>user_id<br/>device_type<br/>ingest_type<br/>stream_path<br/>status=live<br/>playback_available<br/>bytes_received<br/>last_sequence<br/>last_chunk_at

  Python->>Python: playback 대상 stream 선택
  Note over Python: playback_available=true인 MEDIAMTX stream만 HLS 대상<br/>HTTP ingest stream은 목록에는 보이지만 playback 대상이 아니다.

  opt verify playback readiness
    Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/live-streams/{recordingSessionId}
    Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token
    Backend->>DB: STREAMING session + repository read 권한 확인
    Backend->>MTX: active path 조회
    Note over Backend,MTX: MediaMTX Control API /v3/paths/list<br/>playback_ready 계산
    Backend-->>Python: detail with playback_ready
  end

  Python->>Backend: POST /api/v1/live-streams/{recordingSessionId}/playback-ticket
  Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token<br/><br/>body 없음

  Backend->>Backend: requireDashboardOrPython
  Backend->>Redis: live cache 확인
  Note over Backend,Redis: key: stream:recording:{recordingSessionId}<br/>required: status=STREAMING, ingestType=MEDIAMTX
  Backend->>DB: repository read 권한 확인

  alt stream hidden or not playable
    Backend-->>Python: 404 Not Found or 409 Conflict
  else ticket issue success
    Backend->>Redis: playback ticket 저장
    Note over Backend,Redis: key: stream:hls-ticket:{playbackTicket}<br/><br/>value fields<br/>recordingSessionId<br/>repositoryId<br/>userId<br/>ingestType=MEDIAMTX<br/>streamPath<br/>status=active<br/><br/>TTL: 600 seconds
    Backend-->>Python: 201 { playback_ticket, playback_ticket_expires_at }
  end

  Python->>Python: direct HLS URL 구성
  Note over Python: hlsPort = /api/v1/info urls.hls_port 또는 fixed 8888<br/>url = http://{serverHost}:{hlsPort}/{stream_path}/index.m3u8?ticket={playback_ticket}

  Python->>MTX: GET /live/{repo}/{recordingSessionId}/index.m3u8?ticket=pt_...
  Note over Python,MTX: 가능한 경우 모든 playlist/segment 요청에<br/>Authorization: Bearer pt_... header도 같이 전송한다.

  MTX->>Backend: POST /api/v1/auth/mediamtx
  Note over MTX,Backend: MediaMTX authHTTPAddress payload<br/>action=read 또는 playback<br/>protocol=hls<br/>path=live/{repo}/{recordingSessionId}<br/>token=pt_... 또는 query=ticket=pt_...

  Backend->>Redis: playback ticket + live cache 검증
  Note over Backend,Redis: DB-free hot path<br/>1. stream:hls-ticket:{ticket} exists<br/>2. ticket.status=active<br/>3. ticket.ingestType=MEDIAMTX<br/>4. ticket.streamPath == path<br/>5. stream:recording:{recordingSessionId} exists<br/>6. live cache status=STREAMING<br/>7. live cache ingestType=MEDIAMTX<br/>8. repositoryId/path match<br/>9. ticket TTL refresh to 600s

  alt ticket invalid or stream inactive
    Backend-->>MTX: 401 Unauthorized
    MTX-->>Python: HLS request rejected
  else ticket valid
    Backend-->>MTX: 200 OK
    MTX-->>Python: playlist or fMP4 segment bytes
  end

  loop while playback continues
    Python->>MTX: media playlist / fMP4 segment request
    MTX->>Backend: POST /api/v1/auth/mediamtx
    Backend->>Redis: Redis-only validation + TTL refresh
    Backend-->>MTX: 200 OK
    MTX-->>Python: playlist or fMP4 bytes
  end

%% 참고:
%% Python playback ticket 발급은 ef_ static token으로 수행한다.
%% completed video manifest(/api/v1/repositories/{repoId}/manifest) 흐름과 live HLS playback은 별개다.
%% Python HLS client는 segment request까지 ticket이 전달되도록 Authorization: Bearer playback_ticket header를 매 요청에 붙이는 방식을 우선한다.
%% query ticket만 붙인 URL은 일부 HLS client에서 segment request까지 query가 유지되지 않을 수 있으므로 header 병행을 권장한다.
%% HLS bytes는 Caddy를 거치지 않고 MediaMTX 8888/tcp에서 직접 받는다.
%% Caddy /hls route와 legacy HLS auth endpoint는 현재 구조에 없다.
